Tracy Mutinhiri bụ osote minista na-ahụ maka ọrụ na ọdịmma ọha na eze na Zimbabwe. Ọ bụ onye otu House of Assembly maka Marondera East (ZANU-PF).
Kemgbe afọ 2009, a na-ekwu na Mutinhiri nwere ọmịiko na pati MDC
Nke a emeela ka ụdị egwu na nsogbu dị iche iche na ya, ọkachasị mgbe a họpụtara Lovemore Moyo ọzọ dị ka onye na-ekwuchitere ndị omeiwu na ngwụcha Machị 2011
Na ntuli aka a, a na-enyo Mutinhiri enyo na ọ bụ otu n'ime vootu abụọ ZANU-PF na-akwado onye MDC. Mwakpo ahụ gụnyekwara ịnwa ịwakpo ugbo ya na Marondera.
E deberè ya na ndepụta mmachibido iwu nke European Union site na 2007 ruo 2011.
